We utilize the following data sources:

* Roads: [GloBio](https://www.globio.info/download-grip-dataset);
* Airports: [OCHA](https://data.humdata.org/dataset/global-airports);
* Food Insecurity: [FEWS NET](https://fews.net/data/acute-food-insecurity?field_data_node_dates_end_value=&date=&region%5B%5D=535);
* Kenya Red Cross Branches: [Kenya Red Cross](https://www.redcross.or.ke/regions-and-branches/);
* Population: [WorldPop](https://www.worldpop.org/datacatalog/)

We are working on adding more data layers based on the needs of the app's end users.
